  "message": "\u2728 Enhance Events dashboard with tabs, charts, and timeline view\n\n- Add tabbed interface (Overview, Timeline, All Events)\n- Add donut charts for event types, reasons, and cluster distribution\n- Add bar chart for 24-hour event activity\n- Add visual timeline view with event grouping\n- Add quick stats cards (total, warnings, normal, last hour)\n- Make stats cards clickable to filter by type\n- Add auto-refresh toggle in header\n- Streamline filters in list view\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
